titleNullable: AAJ TAK HINDI NEWS DEBATE SHOW "HALLA BOL" TOPICS
subtitleNullable: Listed debate topics of show "Halla Bol" at India News Channel AAJ TAK
descriptionNullable:
हल्‍ला बोल (Halla Bol) is a debate show at Indian Hindi News Channel "[**AAJ TAK**](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aaj_Tak)" which is currently hosted by **[Anjana Om Kashyap](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anjana_Om_Kashyap)**.

This dataset lists topics of 273 debate shows "हल्‍ला बोल"  from 13-09-2022 to 28-07-2023.

See Repo for this project : [**AAJ_TAK_DEBATE**](https://github.com/shivam-maurya-git/Web-Scrapping)

**Note : Topics of Debates are in Hindi Language.**
